<br>
If you're strapped for cash as well as xp, I reccomend doing this quest:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2200">everquest.allakhazam.com/...quest=2200</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Doing that quest, I get about 4 blues each trip. With agnostic Erudite faction, the pieces cost me about 28 plat, and he gives you 60, so you make a profit of 32 plat per trip as well. A little slower than killing HG's used to be, but I think they've nerfed the amount of plat you can make from HG's. Amazingly easy to do. If you bind right beside of the guy you buy from in Thurg, you can seriously decrease the amount of time it takes to do the quest. If the ulthorks are camped, or I can't get/afford a KEI, I'll do this quest for awhile. Takes about 10-15 minutes to run it once depending on your zone times.<br>
